<h2 class="bold font-l">Sonny Corleone Killed</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
The rival gangs really really hated Sonny Corleone. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/ThereIsNoKillLikeOverkill" class='trope-example-link'>There Is No Kill Like Overkill</a></p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="w56nuj" data-video-descrip="Two hitmen try to kill the Godfather, the top mob boss in New York.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;" data-video-title="The Godfather shot" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/w56nuj_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/w56nuj.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/AssassinationAttempt" data-video-tropename="Assassination Attempt" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Film/TheGodfather" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/w56nuj.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">The Godfather shot</span></p>
</a>
</div>
